title: Static Gk

description: Static GK (General Knowledge) refers to facts that do not change over time, such as countries, capitals, historical events, books, important dates, and national symbols.It helps assess a candidateâ€™s awareness of foundational topics. title: Node Js
author: Bharat Kumar
description: Node.js is a powerful, open-source runtime environment that allows JavaScript to run on the server side. Built on Chrome's V8 engine, it enables fast, event-driven, and scalable network applications. It's widely used for building APIs, web apps, and real-time services.
